The Controls
------------

Loading:  Insert disk into drive and swith on.
Press FIRE on opening screen and select difficulty level by moving joystick up
or dowm.  Press FIRE to select.

Controls(Joystick only):

Left		-Walk left
Right		-Walk right
Up		-Jump up
Down		-Crouch/Go down hole
Up & Left	-Jump left
Up & Right	-Jump right
P		-Pause game, any other key restarts.

Other controls(Joystick only):

With FIRE pressed:

Fire + up	-High kick
Fire + right	-Standing kick
Fire + down	-Low kick
Fire + left	-Punch
Fire + up +right-Hit with stick.



